Class CompositionRoot

java.lang.Object
ca.gc.cra.radar.config.CompositionRoot
public final class CompositionRoot extends Object
Temporary composition root used while migrating to the new architecture. It currently exposes stubbed use cases and will be populated with real wiring in subsequent steps.

  • Constructor Summary

    Description
